   "source": [
    "(Odd or Even) Use if statements to determine whether an integer is odd or even.\n",
    "[Hint: Use the remainder operator. An even number is a multiple of 2. Any multiple of 2\n",
    "leaves a remainder of 0 when divided by 2.]"
   ]
  },
